						               													<description>From the publisher:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Gruffalo's Child is feeling brave so she tiptoes out of the gruffalo cave...Race around the board with the Gruffalo's child using colour recognition and counting. This Big Bad Mouse board game is based on the popular book series The Gruffalo's Child. Discover what happens when the Gruffalo's Child visits Snake, Owl, Fox and Mouse. The idea of the game is to make it back to the safety of the gruffalo cave, but beware, there is a Big Bad Mouse lurking in these woods who enjoys nothing more than a slice of Gruffalo pie! Spin the spinner and turn over the top card from the centre of the board that matches the colour on the spinner. If the card selected has footprints on it, move your Gruffalo's Child playing piece forward. The card may have 1, 2 or 3 footprints. This game has strong educational components and helps children learn through social interaction as well as taking turns and co-operation, all whilst having great fun.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
